### 4. JWT Service (`security` package)

#### [NEW] `security/JwtService.java`

Responsibility: all JWT operations. Methods:
- `generateAccessToken(UserDetails)` ‚Üí signed JWT with subject=username, role claim, 15-min expiry
- `generateRefreshToken(UserDetails)` ‚Üí signed JWT with subject=username, 7-day expiry
- `extractUsername(String token)` ‚Üí parses the subject claim
- `isTokenValid(String token, UserDetails)` ‚Üí validates signature + expiration + username match
- `extractClaim(String token, Function)` ‚Üí generic claim extractor

Uses HMAC-SHA256 (`HS256`) with the configured secret key.

